search_results.title: Yolanda Wisher
search_results.snippet: Yolanda Wisher (born 1976) is an American poet, educator and spoken word artist who focuses on the experience of being African-American.

search_results.title: Yolanda Young
search_results.snippet: Yolanda Young (born October 31, 1968) is an American journalist, author, and lecturer. Her work as a writer focuses on law, politics, and culture.
